    <p>Virat Kohli is an Indian international cricketer and captain of the India national team. He is a right-handed batsman. Born and raised in New Delhi, Kohli trained in West Delhi Cricket Academy; started his youth career with Delhi Under-15 team. Kohli made his international debut in 2008 and quickly became a key player in the ODI team.</p>

